If the object of their affection didn't reciprocate the shapeshifter's feelings, than the shapeshifter wouldn't fall in love again. In the case of the shapeshifter Jon Tulane, Jon fell in love with Sandra.

Jon met Sandra through an online dating website.  Yes, there are shapeshifters on Tinder. Many will live their life as a regular human and rarely shapeshift into anyone else.  Typically, shapeshifters will fall in love with only one person in their lifetime.   If the object of their affection didn't reciprocate the shapeshifter's feelings, than the shapeshifter wouldn't fall in love again. In the case of the shapeshifter Jon Tulane, Jon fell in love with Sandra.

Jon met Sandra through an online dating website.  Yes, there are shapeshifters on Tinder.   When Jon first met Sandra for a date, the date was friendly, but Sandra didn't seem to be romantically interested in Jon.  Jon, on the other hand, was smitten with Sandra.  He loved the way she talked, her intelligence, and her beauty.  When Jon and Sandra's date didn't work out, Jon thought the problem was his physically looks.


on decided to change his appearance. to see if he could woo Sandra.  He shapeshifted into a new form, went by a new name, and found Sandra on Tinder again.  Like before, they went out for a date, but it still didn't work out.   Jon repeated this cycle a four more times with the results being the same.  Jon was convinced that Sandra didn't like him because of his looks.  Foolishly, Jon was focusing on the wrong thing.  He focused on his personality

Many will live their life as a regular human and rarely shapeshift into anyone else.  Typically, shapeshifters will fall in love with only one person in their lifetime.   If the object of their affection didn't reciprocate the shapeshifter's feelings, than the shapeshifter wouldn't fall in love again. In the case of the shapeshifter Jon Tulane, Jon fell in love with Sandra.

Jon met Sandra through an online dating website.  Yes, there are shapeshifters on Tinder.   When Jon first met Sandra for a date, the date was friendly, but Sandra didn't seem to be romantically interested in Jon.  Jon, on the other hand, was smitten with Sandra.  He loved the way she talked, her intelligence, and her beauty.  When Jon and Sandra's date didn't work out, Jon thought the problem was his physically looks.


on decided to change his appearance. to see if he could woo Sandra.  He shapeshifted into a new form, went by a new name, and found Sandra on Tinder again. If the object of their affection didn't reciprocate the shapeshifter's feelings, than the shapeshifter wouldn't fall in love again. In the case of the shapeshifter Jon Tulane, Jon fell in love with Sandra.

Jon met Sandra through an online dating website.  Yes, there are shapeshifters on Tinder.   When Jon first met Sandra for a date, the date was friendly, but Sandra didn't seem to be romantically interested in Jon.  Jon, on the other hand, was smitten with Sandra.  He loved the way she talked, her intelligence, and her beauty.  When Jon and Sandra's date didn't work out, Jon thought the problem was his physically looks.


on decided to change his appearance. to see if he could woo Sandra.  He shapeshifted into a new form, went by a new name, and found Sandra on Tinder again.  Like before, they went out for a date, but it still didn't work out.   Jon repeated this cycle a four more times with the results being the same.  Jon was convinced that Sandra didn't like him because of his looks.  Foolishly, Jon was focusing on the wrong thing.  He focused on his looks as opposed to his personality.

Eventually, Jon gave up trying to court Sandra.  H
